 sau:<img class=\\" wp-image-5705       \\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.muavere.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/Dayweek\\/Bang-gia-Jetstar-cap-nhat-26jul2013.png\\" alt=\\"Jetstar2013\\" width=\\"650\\" height=\\"287\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_5705\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 4px 0px 0px; border: 1px solid #dddddd; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; color: #232323; font-family: Arial, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; width: 660px; background: #f3f3f3;\\">\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 4px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 11px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 17px; background: transparent;\\">Gi\\u00e1 th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a Jetstar trong n\\u0103m 2013. Kh\\u00f4ng \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng cho c\\u00e1c ng\\u00e0y cao \\u0111i\\u1ec3m, l\\u1ec5 t\\u1ebft.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 18px; color: #232323; font-family: Arial, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f7;\\">\\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t hi\\u1ec7n nay \\u0111ang c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 khuy\\u1ebfn m\\u1ea1i nh\\u01b0 sau:<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 4px 0px 0px; border: 1px solid #dddddd; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; color: #232323; font-family: Arial, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; width: 576px; background: #f3f3f3;\\"><img class=\\"   \\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\" title=\\"Gi\\u00e1 hot trong th\\u00e1ng n\\u00e0y.\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.muavere.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/Dayweek\\/gia-hot-Jetstar.png\\" alt=\\"Gi\\u00e1 hot trong th\\u00e1ng n\\u00e0y.\\" width=\\"566\\" height=\\"559\\" \\/>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 4px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 11px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 17px; background: transparent;\\">Gi\\u00e1 hot trong th\\u00e1ng n\\u00e0y.<br \\/>Gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 khuy\\u1ebfn m\\u1ea1i \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng cho m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 chuy\\u1ebfn bay v\\u00e0 ng\\u00e0y bay.<br \\/>Tp. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u2013 \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013<br \\/>Tp. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u2013 Bu\\u00f4n Ma Thu\\u1ed9t: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013<br \\/>Tp. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u2013 H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013<br \\/>Tp. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u2013 H\\u1ea3i Ph\\u00f2ng: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013.<br \\/>Tp. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u2013 Vinh: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013<br \\/>H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i \\u2013 \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013<br \\/>Vinh \\u2013 Bu\\u00f4n Ma Thu\\u1ed9t: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013<br \\/>Ha Noi \\u2013 Nha Trang: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013<br \\/>Tp. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u2013 Singapore: t\\u1eeb 10\\/9\\/2013 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 28\\/11\\/2013<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #3d3d3d; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 1em; font-family: ''OFL Sorts Mill Goudy TT'', Georgia, serif; background: #f7f7f7;\\">C) Gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 m\\u00e1y bay\\u00a0<a style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #808080; background: transparent;\\" title=\\"Vietjet Air\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.muavere.com\\/thong-tin-bo-ich\\/hang-van-chuyen\\/vietjetair\\/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Vietjet Air<\\/a><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 18px; color: #232323; font-family: Arial, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; text-align: center; background: #f7f7f7;\\"><img class=\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6034\\" style=\\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\" title=\\"gia ve may bay Vietjet\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.muavere.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/logo-vietjet.png\\" alt=\\"gia ve may bay Vietjet\\" width=\\"337\\" height=\\"78\\" \\/><br \\/>Do\\u00a0<strong style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1c1c1c; background: transparent;\\">g\\u00eda v\\u00e9 m\\u00e1y bay Vietjet Air<\\/strong>\\u00a0li\\u00ean t\\u1ee5c thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i. \\u0110\\u1eb7t s\\u1edbm gi\\u00e1 r\\u1ebb, \\u0111\\u1eb7t tr\\u1ec5 gi\\u00e1 cao. V\\u00ec v\\u1eady, b\\u1ea1n vui l\\u00f2ng li\\u00ean l\\u1ea1c v\\u1edbi nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean ph\\u00f2ng v\\u00e9 \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u00e1o gi\\u00e1 r\\u1ebb nh\\u1ea5t. D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ee9c gi\\u00e1 th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a Vietjet. T\\u00f9y ng\\u00e0y \\u0111i, t\\u00f9y ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1eb7t v\\u00e9 m\\u00e0 gi\\u00e1 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 kh\\u00e1c nhau.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 4px 0px 0px; border: 1px solid #dddddd; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; color: #232323; font-family: Arial, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; width: 535px; background: #f3f3f3;\\"><img style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\" title=\\"B\\u1ea3ng gi\\u00e1 Vietjet 2013\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.muavere.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/Dayweek\\/Bang-gia-Vietjet-2013.gif\\" alt=\\"B\\u1ea3ng gi\\u00e1 Vietjet 2013\\" width=\\"525\\" height=\\"179\\" \\/>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 4px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 11px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 17px; background: transparent;\\">B\\u1ea3ng gi\\u00e1 Vietjet 2013<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #3d3d3d; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 1em; font-family: ''OFL Sorts Mill Goudy TT'', Georgia, serif; background: #f7f7f7;\\">D) Gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 m\\u00e1y bay\\u00a0<a style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #808080; background: transparent;\\" title=\\"Air Mekong\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.muavere.com\\/thong-tin-bo-ich\\/hang-van-chuyen\\/airmekong\\/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">AirMekong<\\/a><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 18px; color: #232323; font-family: Arial, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f7;\\">T\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1 nh\\u01b0 Viejet Air v\\u00e0 Jetstar, Air Mekong gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 li\\u00ean t\\u1ee5c thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i. V\\u00ec Air Mekong \\u0111ang ng\\u1eebng bay \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u1ea1ch \\u0111\\u1ecbnh chi\\u1ebfn l\\u01b0\\u1ee3c kinh doanh v\\u00e0 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u00e0u bay n\\u00ean t\\u1ea1m th\\u1eddi qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch vui l\\u00f2ng \\u0111\\u1eb7t v\\u00e9 c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c h\\u00e3ng thay th\\u1ebf kh\\u00e1c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #3d3d3d; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 1em; font-family: ''OFL Sorts Mill Goudy TT'', Georgia, serif; background: #f7f7f7;\\">E) Gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 m\\u00e1y bay qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf \\u0111i Ch\\u00e2u \\u00c1, ch\\u00e2u \\u00dac, ch\\u00e2u M\\u1ef9, ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u, ch\\u00e2u Phi<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 18px; color: #232323; font-family: Arial, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f7;\\">\\u0110\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 m\\u00e1y bay gi\\u1ea3m, gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 m\\u00e1y bay khuy\\u1ebfn m\\u1ea1i ho\\u1eb7c gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 m\\u00e1y bay \\u01b0u \\u0111\\u00e3i c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c h\\u00e3ng h\\u00e0ng kh\\u00f4ng Qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf nh\\u01b0 Evar Air, China Airlines, All Nippon Airways, Cathay Pacific, Quatar Airways, Air France, Thai Airways\\u2026vui l\\u00f2ng li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u1ea1i l\\u00fd ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 m\\u1ee9c gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea1nh tranh m\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c h\\u00e3ng h\\u00e0ng kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u01b0u \\u00e1i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 18px; color: #232323; font-family: Arial, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f7;\\"><strong style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1c1c1c; background: transparent;\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #ff0000; background: transparent;\\">\\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u01b0u \\u00fd:<\\/span><\\/strong>\\u00a0Gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 trong b\\u1ea3ng gi\\u00e1 tr\\u00ean ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u00e3 bao g\\u1ed3m thu\\u1ebf VAT, ph\\u00ed s\\u00e2n bay. Do \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m chung c\\u1ee7a ng\\u00e0nh h\\u00e0ng kh\\u00f4ng n\\u00ean kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3ng gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh